{"abstract": "A new ad from Pfister parodies a classic Calvin Klein Obsession commercial to poke fun at campaigns that portray household faucets as luxury goods.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2014/11/14/business/media/with-a-whisper-pfister-takes-a-comedic-jab-at-highbrow-faucet-commercials.html", "snippet": "A new ad from Pfister parodies a classic Calvin Klein Obsession commercial to poke fun at campaigns that portray household faucets as luxury goods.", "lead_paragraph": "HOUSEHOLD faucets are the essence of functionality, but they are often advertised as luxury goods. Last year, for example, one of the leading faucet brands, Moen, introduced a television commercial in which a model in an evening dress sashays into a bathroom and puts on a gleaming, oversize necklace. The necklace then slips from her neck and, through digital animation, scatters into pieces on the counter, reassembling as a faucet. \u201cStatement piece for your bathroom,\u201d says a voice-over. ", "print_section": "B", "print_page": "4", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/11/14/business/Adco/Adco-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 400, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2014/11/14/business/Adco/Adco-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 400}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/11/14/business/Adco/Adco-jumbo.jpg", "height": 682, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/11/14/business/Adco/Adco-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 1151, "width": 1727, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images